description: A pristine, pale white dock extends from the store and out into the lake, while a variety of small boats are lined up along its sides.  The white walls of the shop glisten with a faint sheen of moisture, and a small door leads back into its cozy interior.  Plants hang from the windowsill of the building, their deep green leaves matching the hue of several lilypads clustered around the dock.
title: [Veythorne Manor, Dockside]
